 ainsi que ses b\u00e9n\u00e9fices. La social data r\u00e9volutionne le marketing en r\u00e9v\u00e9lant des insights. Ils permettent aux marketeurs d\u2019\u00eatre encore plus efficaces en \u00e9mergeant une image toujours plus pr\u00e9cise des consommateurs.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"image-single-wrapper text-center\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/social-media-insights-1.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"Social Media Insights 1\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/social-media-insights-1.png 1920w, https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/social-media-insights-1-300x169.png 300w, https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/social-media-insights-1-768x432.png 768w, https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/social-media-insights-1-1536x864.png 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" \/><\/div>[\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row el_class=&#8221;content-article article-table-matiere&#8221;][vc_column]<div class=\"text-bloc toc\"><p class=\"titre_3\">Table des mati\u00e8res<\/p>\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_74 ez-toc-wrap-center counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-custom ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\" style=\"cursor:inherit\">Sommaire<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" aria-label=\"Toggle Table of Content\"><span class=\"ez-toc-js-icon-con\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2